      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "//-----------SCRIPT INFORMATION-----------//\n/*\nVersion: 1.0.0\nScript Name: Generate System 3D View\nDeveloped by: AECOM MY - Amer Nasir, Tuah Hamid\nDate: 06/03/2025\n\nVersion: 1.1.0\nDate: 11/03/2025\nChange log:\n- Filter elements based on Mechanical Equipment first\n- Allow main system selection, plus, additional systems to add\n\nVersion: 1.1.1\nDate: 21/04/2025\nChange log:\n- Removed FCU from valid system names\n- Brute include mech equipment in elements to be isolated\n*/;"
