      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "input;\nwasRun;\nwasCancelled;\n\nisEmpty = List.IsEmpty(input);\ncheckNulls = input == null;\nisNull = List.AnyTrue(checkNulls);\n\nallowData = [Imperative]{\nif (wasRun == true && wasCancelled == false && isEmpty == false && isNull == false)\n\treturn input;\nelse\n\treturn List.Empty;\n};\n\n//output\nallowData;"
    },
