      "Replication": "Disabled",
      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "allMechEquipments;\ninput;\n\n//get valid equipments\neqNames = Revit.Elements.Element.GetParameterValueByName(allMechEquipments, \"Equipment Name\");\nisValidName = DSCore.String.Contains(eqNames<1L>, input<1L>, false);\ncount = List.Count(allMechEquipments);\nindX = isValidName==true?-1:0..count-1;\nvalidMechEquipments = List.RemoveItemAtIndex(allMechEquipments, indX);\n\n//output\nvalidMechEquipments;\neqCode = input;"
    },
