      "Description": "Allows for DesignScript code to be authored directly",
      "Code": "validMechEquipments;\neqCode;\n\n//get equipment code Id\neqCodeId = Revit.Elements.Element.GetParameterValueByName(validMechEquipments, \"Equipment Code ID\");\nsorted_dict = List.SortByKey(validMechEquipments, eqCodeId);\nsorted_ids = Dictionary.ValueAtKey(sorted_dict, \"sortedKeys\");\nsorted_equipments = Dictionary.ValueAtKey(sorted_dict, \"sortedList\");\ncombEqCode = List.Flatten(eqCode + \"-\" + sorted_ids<1L>, -1);\n\n//output\ncombEqCode;\nsorted_equipments;"
    },
